NAME

DateTime::Locale::ku_TR - Locale data examples for the Kurdish Turkey (ku-TR) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Kurdish Turkey locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 reşemiyê 5, sêşem
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 berfanbarê 22, în
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 rezberê 15, şemî

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 reşemiyê 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 berfanbarê 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 rezberê 15

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 reş 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 ber 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 rez 15

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B
